    "LSC [76] enables agents within a cluster radius to decide whether to become 4 Page 18 of 48 a leader agent.",
    "Then all non-leader agents in the same cluster will only communicate with the leader agent.",
    "NeurComm [83] and IP [84] preset a graph structure among agents built upon networked multi-agent systems.",
    "In both NeurComm and IP, communicatees are restricted to neighbors on the graph.",
    "Net-SA-GS-MG [39] uses a pre-trained graph to limit communication and restricts communication on neighboring agents."
  ],
